          }
        },
        "text_9AGHNn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>RB Mitti Store carries forward a tradition that began generations before us. What started with hands shaping raw clay in a small family workshop has grown into a trusted name in natural, handcrafted kitchenware — bringing that same craftsmanship to homes across Pakistan.</p>",
            "color": "#121212"
          }
        },
        "text_FVikwA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><br/>We don't rely on factories or mass production — each item is shaped by hand, dried naturally, and fired the traditional way, exactly as it was taught to us. That knowledge shows in the durability, the finish, and the authenticity of every piece that leaves our workshop.<br/><br/></p>",
            "color": "#121212"
          }
        }
