          }
        },
        "heading_JHf8NJ": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "\"This isn't a business I started — it's a craft I inherited from my great-grandfather, and it runs through everything we make today.\"",
            "color": "#000000"
          }
        },
        "text_rC7RHU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>RB Mitti Store is run today by Muhammad Shakir, who continues a craft passed down through three generations of his family. What began with his great-grandfather working clay by hand was carried forward through his grandfather, and now continues under his leadership.</p>",
            "color": "#121212"
          }
        },
        "text_VRJyt3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Growing up around this craft, Muhammad Shakir learned more than technique — he learned patience, respect for natural materials, and the discipline of doing things the honest way, even as the wider market shifted toward mass-produced, chemical-coated alternatives.</p>",
            "color": "#121212"
          }
        },
        "text_NFWMi7": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Today, RB Mitti Store brings that inherited craftsmanship to homes across Pakistan — natural clay, marble, and wooden kitchenware, made the same honest way it always has been.<br/></p>",
            "color": "#121212"
          }
        },
        "quote_box_EfjKFz": {
          "type": "quote_box",
          "settings": {
            "text": "\"This isn't a business I started — it's a craft I inherited from my great-grandfather, and it runs through everything we make today.\"",
